data.description: Welcome to 130 Joe Fletcher Drive in Madison! This full brick, well maintained home in the Terrace at Savannah is low maintenance and move-in ready. This home has a split bedroom floorplan with the owner's suite at the back of the home. The owner's suite features a spacious bedroom, walk-in closet, double vanity and a soaking tub. The open concept in the living room, dining room and kitchen is great for gatherings with family and friends. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances and lots of counter space. Down the hall is a full bathroom, laundry room and two additional bedrooms. Step out the back door to the fenced in back yard with an extended patio featuring a built-in firepit. This home is located just 5 miles from Huntsville International Airport and just 10 miles to the Redstone Arsenal Gate 9. If you're looking for low maintenance and convenience, this is it! Zoned for Bob Jones High School, Journey Middle School and Midtown Elementary School.
